headline: Old Dominion Freight Line Provides Update for First Quarter 2025
summary: THOMASVILLE, N.C., March 04, 2025--Old Dominion Freight Line, Inc. (Nasdaq: ODFL) today reported certain less-than-truckload ("LTL") operating metrics for February 2025. Revenue per day decreased 5.0% as compared to February 2024 due to a 7.1% decrease in LTL tons per day that was partially offset by an increase in LTL revenue per hundredweight.
